abstract: The Arizona Diamondbacks hitting coach Don Baylor, who spent the night at a local hospital after a fainting in the clubhouse Friday, will be back in the dugout Saturday night.
snippet: The Arizona Diamondbacks hitting coach Don Baylor, who spent the night at a local hospital after a fainting in the clubhouse Friday, will be back in the dugout Saturday night.
lead_paragraph: MILWAUKEE - The Arizona Diamondbacks hitting coach Don Baylor, who spent the night at a hospital after a fainting in the clubhouse Friday, returned to Miller Park on Saturday morning and brushed aside all concerns with one meaty arm.
